channel.title: Listen to My NEwest Song- Quest For Bits!!!
channel.description:
The links below, listen now! :wink:
[url]https://soundcloud.com/teksaur/quest-for-bits[/url]
So Quest For Bits is my newest song in probably 7 weeks during which I've been experimenting with new vst's and learning a bunch of effects and production styles to help spice up my music. This is the first song I used Ozone Isotope to master the whole thing, and it turned out to be pretty amazing.
If there's any other people who make music here I'd gladly appreciate feedback. Hope you like the song!

item.title: Listen to My NEwest Song- Quest For Bits!!!
item.dc:creator: CPU
item.description:
Keep in mind, this is just a personal opinion. Don’t take it personally.

I found it to have too many midtones. The beginning would have sounded better with an echo chamber effect.

Overall, the sound lacks dynamics and showed too much repetitiveness.
